Class WeightedDiagraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.pw.elka.gis.desp.model.WeightedDiagraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class WeightedDiagraph
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Data type for representing weighted diagraph. This representation maintain a node indexed list of lists of DirectedEdge objects.
